#. <section class="sutta" id="mn6"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "mn6:0.1"
msgid "Majjhima Nikāya 6"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "mn6:0.2"
msgid "Ākaṅkheyyasutta"
msgstr ""

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya1"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli1.33"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
#. <span class="evam">
msgctxt "mn6:1.1"
msgid "Evaṃ me sutaṃ—​"
msgstr ""

#. </span>
msgctxt "mn6:1.2"
msgid ""
"ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn6:1.3"
msgid "Tatra kho bhagavā bhikkhū āmantesi:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn6:1.4"
msgid "“bhikkhavo”ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn6:1.5"
msgid "“Bhadante”ti te bhikkhū bhagavato paccassosuṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn6:1.6"
msgid "Bhagavā etadavoca:"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya2"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "mn6:2.1"
msgid ""
"“Sampannasīlā, bhikkhave, viharatha sampannapātimokkhā; "
"pātimokkhasaṃvarasaṃvutā viharatha ācāragocarasampannā aṇumattesu vajjesu "
"bhayadassāvino; samādāya sikkhatha sikkhāpadesu."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya3"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
#. VAR: manāpo ca garu ca bhāvanīyo cā’ti → manāpo garu bhāvanīyo cāti (bj, pts1)
msgctxt "mn6:3.1"
msgid ""
"Ākaṅkheyya ce, bhikkhave, bhikkhu: ‘sabrahmacārīnaṃ piyo ca assaṃ manāpo ca "
"garu ca bhāvanīyo cā’ti, sīlesvevassa paripūrakārī ajjhattaṃ "
"cetosamathamanuyutto anirākatajjhāno vipassanāya samannāgato brūhetā "
"suññāgārānaṃ. (1)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya4"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "mn6:4.1"
msgid ""
"Ākaṅkheyya ce, bhikkhave, bhikkhu: ‘lābhī assaṃ "
"cīvarapiṇḍapātasenāsanagilānappaccayabhesajjaparikkhārānan’ti, sīlesvevassa "
"paripūrakārī ajjhattaṃ cetosamathamanuyutto anirākatajjhāno vipassanāya "
"samannāgato brūhetā suññāgārānaṃ. (2)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya5"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "mn6:5.1"
msgid ""
"Ākaṅkheyya ce, bhikkhave, bhikkhu: ‘yesāhaṃ "
"cīvarapiṇḍapātasenāsanagilānappaccayabhesajjaparikkhāraṃ paribhuñjāmi tesaṃ "
"te kārā mahapphalā assu mahānisaṃsā’ti, sīlesvevassa paripūrakārī ajjhattaṃ "
"cetosamathamanuyutto anirākatajjhāno vipassanāya samannāgato brūhetā "
"suññāgārānaṃ. (3)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya6"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
#. VAR: kālaṅkatā → kālakatā (bj, s1-3, pts1)
msgctxt "mn6:6.1"
msgid ""
"Ākaṅkheyya ce, bhikkhave, bhikkhu: ‘ye maṃ ñātī sālohitā petā kālaṅkatā "
"pasannacittā anussaranti tesaṃ taṃ mahapphalaṃ assa mahānisaṃsan’ti, "
"sīlesvevassa paripūrakārī ajjhattaṃ cetosamathamanuyutto anirākatajjhāno "
"vipassanāya samannāgato brūhetā suññāgārānaṃ. (4)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya7"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "mn6:7.1"
msgid ""
"Ākaṅkheyya ce, bhikkhave, bhikkhu: ‘aratiratisaho assaṃ, na ca maṃ arati "
"saheyya, uppannaṃ aratiṃ abhibhuyya abhibhuyya vihareyyan’ti, sīlesvevassa "
"paripūrakārī … pe … brūhetā suññāgārānaṃ. (5)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya8"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc8"></a>
msgctxt "mn6:8.1"
msgid ""
"Ākaṅkheyya ce, bhikkhave, bhikkhu: ‘bhayabheravasaho assaṃ, na ca maṃ "
"bhayabheravaṃ saheyya, uppannaṃ bhayabheravaṃ abhibhuyya abhibhuyya "
"vihareyyan’ti, sīlesvevassa paripūrakārī … pe … brūhetā suññāgārānaṃ. (6)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya9"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc9"></a>
msgctxt "mn6:9.1"
msgid ""
"Ākaṅkheyya ce, bhikkhave, bhikkhu: ‘catunnaṃ jhānānaṃ ābhicetasikānaṃ "
"diṭṭhadhammasukhavihārānaṃ nikāmalābhī assaṃ akicchalābhī akasiralābhī’ti, "
"sīlesvevassa paripūrakārī … pe … brūhetā suññāgārānaṃ. (7)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya10"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc10"></a>
msgctxt "mn6:10.1"
msgid ""
"Ākaṅkheyya ce, bhikkhave, bhikkhu: ‘ye te santā vimokkhā atikkamma rūpe "
"āruppā, te kāyena phusitvā vihareyyan’ti, sīlesvevassa paripūrakārī … pe … "
"brūhetā suññāgārānaṃ. (8)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya11"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli1.34"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc11"></a>
msgctxt "mn6:11.1"
msgid ""
"Ākaṅkheyya ce, bhikkhave, bhikkhu: ‘tiṇṇaṃ saṃyojanānaṃ parikkhayā sotāpanno "
"assaṃ avinipātadhammo niyato sambodhiparāyaṇo’ti, sīlesvevassa paripūrakārī …"
" pe … brūhetā suññāgārānaṃ. (9)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya12"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc12"></a>
msgctxt "mn6:12.1"
msgid ""
"Ākaṅkheyya ce, bhikkhave, bhikkhu: ‘tiṇṇaṃ saṃyojanānaṃ parikkhayā "
"rāgadosamohānaṃ tanuttā sakadāgāmī assaṃ sakideva imaṃ lokaṃ āgantvā "
"dukkhassantaṃ kareyyan’ti, sīlesvevassa paripūrakārī … pe … brūhetā "
"suññāgārānaṃ. (10)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya13"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc13"></a>
msgctxt "mn6:13.1"
msgid ""
"Ākaṅkheyya ce, bhikkhave, bhikkhu: ‘pañcannaṃ orambhāgiyānaṃ saṃyojanānaṃ "
"parikkhayā opapātiko assaṃ tattha parinibbāyī anāvattidhammo tasmā lokā’ti, "
"sīlesvevassa paripūrakārī … pe … brūhetā suññāgārānaṃ. (11)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya14"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc14"></a>
msgctxt "mn6:14.1"
msgid ""
"Ākaṅkheyya ce, bhikkhave, bhikkhu: ‘anekavihitaṃ iddhividhaṃ "
"paccanubhaveyyaṃ—ekopi hutvā bahudhā assaṃ, bahudhāpi hutvā eko assaṃ; "
"āvibhāvaṃ tirobhāvaṃ; tirokuṭṭaṃ tiropākāraṃ tiropabbataṃ asajjamāno "
"gaccheyyaṃ, seyyathāpi ākāse; pathaviyāpi ummujjanimujjaṃ kareyyaṃ, "
"seyyathāpi udake; udakepi abhijjamāne gaccheyyaṃ, seyyathāpi pathaviyaṃ; "
"ākāsepi pallaṅkena kameyyaṃ, seyyathāpi pakkhī sakuṇo; imepi candimasūriye "
"evaṃmahiddhike evaṃmahānubhāve pāṇinā parāmaseyyaṃ parimajjeyyaṃ; yāva "
"brahmalokāpi kāyena vasaṃ vatteyyan’ti, sīlesvevassa paripūrakārī … pe … "
"brūhetā suññāgārānaṃ. (12)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya15"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc15"></a>
msgctxt "mn6:15.1"
msgid ""
"Ākaṅkheyya ce, bhikkhave, bhikkhu: ‘dibbāya sotadhātuyā visuddhāya "
"atikkantamānusikāya ubho sadde suṇeyyaṃ—dibbe ca mānuse ca ye dūre santike "
"cā’ti, sīlesvevassa paripūrakārī … pe … brūhetā suññāgārānaṃ. (13)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya16"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli1.35"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc16"></a>
msgctxt "mn6:16.1"
msgid ""
"Ākaṅkheyya ce, bhikkhave, bhikkhu: ‘parasattānaṃ parapuggalānaṃ cetasā ceto "
"paricca pajāneyyaṃ—sarāgaṃ vā cittaṃ sarāgaṃ cittanti pajāneyyaṃ, vītarāgaṃ "
"vā cittaṃ vītarāgaṃ cittanti pajāneyyaṃ; sadosaṃ vā cittaṃ sadosaṃ cittanti "
"pajāneyyaṃ, vītadosaṃ vā cittaṃ vītadosaṃ cittanti pajāneyyaṃ; samohaṃ vā "
"cittaṃ samohaṃ cittanti pajāneyyaṃ, vītamohaṃ vā cittaṃ vītamohaṃ cittanti "
"pajāneyyaṃ; saṅkhittaṃ vā cittaṃ saṅkhittaṃ cittanti pajāneyyaṃ, vikkhittaṃ "
"vā cittaṃ vikkhittaṃ cittanti pajāneyyaṃ; mahaggataṃ vā cittaṃ mahaggataṃ "
"cittanti pajāneyyaṃ, amahaggataṃ vā cittaṃ amahaggataṃ cittanti pajāneyyaṃ; "
"sauttaraṃ vā cittaṃ sauttaraṃ cittanti pajāneyyaṃ, anuttaraṃ vā cittaṃ "
"anuttaraṃ cittanti pajāneyyaṃ; samāhitaṃ vā cittaṃ samāhitaṃ cittanti "
"pajāneyyaṃ, asamāhitaṃ vā cittaṃ asamāhitaṃ cittanti pajāneyyaṃ; vimuttaṃ vā "
"cittaṃ vimuttaṃ cittanti pajāneyyaṃ, avimuttaṃ vā cittaṃ avimuttaṃ cittanti "
"pajāneyyan’ti, "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn6:16.2"
msgid "sīlesvevassa paripūrakārī … pe … brūhetā suññāgārānaṃ. (14)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya17"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc17"></a>
msgctxt "mn6:17.1"
msgid ""
"Ākaṅkheyya ce, bhikkhave, bhikkhu: ‘anekavihitaṃ pubbenivāsaṃ anussareyyaṃ, "
"seyyathidaṃ—ekampi jātiṃ dvepi jātiyo tissopi jātiyo catassopi jātiyo "
"pañcapi jātiyo dasapi jātiyo vīsampi jātiyo tiṃsampi jātiyo cattālīsampi "
"jātiyo paññāsampi jātiyo jātisatampi jātisahassampi jāti satasahassampi "
"anekepi saṃvaṭṭakappe anekepi vivaṭṭakappe anekepi saṃvaṭṭavivaṭṭakappe—"
"amutrāsiṃ evaṃnāmo evaṅgotto evaṃvaṇṇo evamāhāro evaṃsukhadukkhappaṭisaṃvedī "
"evamāyupariyanto, so tato cuto amutra udapādiṃ; tatrāpāsiṃ evaṃnāmo "
"evaṅgotto evaṃvaṇṇo evamāhāro evaṃsukhadukkhappaṭisaṃvedī evamāyupariyanto, "
"so tato cuto idhūpapannoti. Iti sākāraṃ sauddesaṃ anekavihitaṃ pubbenivāsaṃ "
"anussareyyan’ti, "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn6:17.2"
msgid "sīlesvevassa paripūrakārī … pe … brūhetā suññāgārānaṃ. (15)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya18"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc18"></a>
msgctxt "mn6:18.1"
msgid ""
"Ākaṅkheyya ce, bhikkhave, bhikkhu: ‘dibbena cakkhunā visuddhena "
"atikkantamānusakena satte passeyyaṃ cavamāne upapajjamāne hīne paṇīte "
"suvaṇṇe dubbaṇṇe sugate duggate yathākammūpage satte pajāneyyaṃ—ime vata "
"bhonto sattā kāyaduccaritena samannāgatā vacīduccaritena samannāgatā "
"manoduccaritena samannāgatā ariyānaṃ upavādakā micchādiṭṭhikā "
"micchādiṭṭhikammasamādānā, te kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā apāyaṃ duggatiṃ "
"vinipātaṃ nirayaṃ upapannā; ime vā pana bhonto sattā kāyasucaritena "
"samannāgatā vacīsucaritena samannāgatā manosucaritena samannāgatā ariyānaṃ "
"anupavādakā sammādiṭṭhikā sammādiṭṭhikammasamādānā, te kāyassa bhedā paraṃ "
"maraṇā sugatiṃ saggaṃ lokaṃ upapannāti, iti dibbena cakkhunā visuddhena "
"atikkantamānusakena satte passeyyaṃ cavamāne upapajjamāne hīne paṇīte "
"suvaṇṇe dubbaṇṇe sugate duggate yathākammūpage satte pajāneyyan’ti, "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn6:18.2"
msgid ""
"sīlesvevassa paripūrakārī ajjhattaṃ cetosamathamanuyutto anirākatajjhāno "
"vipassanāya samannāgato brūhetā suññāgārānaṃ. (16)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya19"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli1.36"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc19"></a>
msgctxt "mn6:19.1"
msgid ""
"Ākaṅkheyya ce, bhikkhave, bhikkhu: ‘āsavānaṃ khayā anāsavaṃ cetovimuttiṃ "
"paññāvimuttiṃ diṭṭheva dhamme sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā upasampajja "
"vihareyyan’ti, "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn6:19.2"
msgid ""
"sīlesvevassa paripūrakārī ajjhattaṃ cetosamathamanuyutto anirākatajjhāno "
"vipassanāya samannāgato brūhetā suññāgārānaṃ. (17)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya20"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc20"></a>
msgctxt "mn6:20.1"
msgid ""
"‘Sampannasīlā, bhikkhave, viharatha sampannapātimokkhā; "
"pātimokkhasaṃvarasaṃvutā viharatha ācāragocarasampannā aṇumattesu vajjesu "
"bhayadassāvino; samādāya sikkhatha sikkhāpadesū’ti—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn6:20.2"
msgid "iti yaṃ taṃ vuttaṃ idametaṃ paṭicca vuttan”ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc21"></a>
msgctxt "mn6:20.3"
msgid "Idamavoca bhagavā."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn6:20.4"
msgid "Attamanā te bhikkhū bhagavato bhāsitaṃ abhinandunti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "mn6:20.5"
msgid "Ākaṅkheyyasuttaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ chaṭṭhaṃ."
msgstr ""
